719
00:56:28,490 --> 00:56:29,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana kau semalam?</font>

720
00:56:30,020 --> 00:56:32,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membunuh orang lain lagi setelah lolos dari kami?</font>

721
00:56:32,460 --> 00:56:36,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengamuk hanya karena aku menyiapkan teh?</font>

722
00:56:37,520 --> 00:56:38,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa katamu, bangsat?</font>

723
00:56:38,920 --> 00:56:42,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, kelihatannya ada wanita yang mati lagi.</font>

724
00:56:43,820 --> 00:56:45,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangsat kau...</font>

725
00:56:45,220 --> 00:56:46,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Bajingan.</font>

726
00:57:05,560 --> 00:57:07,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Mati. Kau harus mati.</font>

727
00:57:07,890 --> 00:57:10,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Mati. Kau pantas mati.</font>

728
00:57:15,620 --> 00:57:17,660
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bisa-bisanya kau...
- Lepaskan! Lepaskan!</font>

729
00:57:17,660 --> 00:57:19,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, lepaskan dia!</font>

730
00:57:20,390 --> 00:57:22,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan! Kubilang lepaskan!</font>

731
00:57:22,190 --> 00:57:23,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan! Sialan.</font>

732
00:57:23,490 --> 00:57:26,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kemari kau! Lepaskan!</font>

733
00:57:46,420 --> 00:57:47,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada yang ingin kau katakan padaku?</font>

734
00:57:52,490 --> 00:57:55,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah, kira-kira apa yang sebaiknya kukatakan padamu?</font>

735
00:58:02,760 --> 00:58:04,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mendekatiku karena tahu segalanya?</font>

736
00:58:06,590 --> 00:58:08,890
<font color=#FFFF00>7 tahun lalu, pertama kalinya kita bertemu di TKP...</font>

737
00:58:09,990 --> 00:58:11,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengerti maksud ucapanmu.</font>

738
00:58:13,520 --> 00:58:15,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau memang merasa aku pelakunya,</font>

739
00:58:16,220 --> 00:58:17,660
<font color=#FFFF00>bawakan buktinya.</font>

740
00:58:24,860 --> 00:58:25,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar.</font>

741
00:58:31,490 --> 00:58:35,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menyerah meski kau mengambil langkah yang bodoh.</font>

742
00:58:38,460 --> 00:58:41,590
