771
01:00:25,590 --> 01:00:27,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada memori lain yang muncul.</font>

772
01:00:42,290 --> 01:00:46,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"N, O, E, L".</i></font>

773
01:00:49,320 --> 01:00:50,320
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Yeon Ho-ya.</i></font>

774
01:00:50,760 --> 01:00:52,520
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Eomma.</i></font>

775
01:00:52,690 --> 01:00:56,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini tulisannya "N, O, E, L", 'kan?</i></font>

776
01:00:56,690 --> 01:00:57,690
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Yeon Ho-ya.</i></font>

777
01:00:58,290 --> 01:01:00,320
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau tidak boleh sembarangan menyentuh ini.</i></font>

778
01:01:00,320 --> 01:01:01,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa?</i></font>

779
01:01:01,360 --> 01:01:02,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini milik Appa.</i></font>

780
01:01:02,760 --> 01:01:03,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Appa?</i></font>

781
01:01:04,060 --> 01:01:05,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya.</i></font>

782
01:01:05,420 --> 01:01:09,120
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia tidak tahu kapan waktunya,
tapi suatu saat pasti ia butuhkan.</i></font>

783
01:01:09,390 --> 01:01:11,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak bolehkah ini buat aku?</i></font>

784
01:01:11,690 --> 01:01:13,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku ingin menyimpannya.</i></font>

785
01:01:14,520 --> 01:01:17,890
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak boleh. Eomma harus minta izin dulu sebelum memberikannya.</i></font>

786
01:01:19,690 --> 01:01:22,220
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kalau begitu...</i></font>

787
01:01:22,220 --> 01:01:24,060
<font color=#FFFF00><i>kita sembunyikan di tempat yang hanya Yeon Ho dan Eomma saja yang tahu?</i></font>

788
01:01:24,960 --> 01:01:27,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kita bisa main "cari harta karun" saat Appa pulang.</i></font>

789
01:01:27,920 --> 01:01:30,260
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Cari harta karun? Oke.</i></font>

790
01:01:31,690 --> 01:01:34,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar itu bolpoin yang sama.
